  "description": "A hummingbird is captured in mid-flight, seemingly suspended near a tall, vibrant orange and brown flower stalk. The hummingbird's wings are blurred, indicating rapid movement, and its beak appears to be probing one of the florets. The flower stalk is composed of numerous tightly clustered blooms. The background is a soft, out-of-focus blend of blue and green, creating a bokeh effect with diffused light spots. The lighting is soft and appears to be natural daylight, highlighting the texture of the flower and the delicate features of the hummingbird.",
